{"tid":656444,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大S終止懷孕第三胎","createTime":"2018-05-07T09:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T12:38:56.000Z","uid":82917,"like":23,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b75ef120427c12fb64af856bfad2d7ea207f1d32","tid":656444,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/172127_03039eaf1726d676759336b1513c173c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F172127_03039eaf1726d676759336b1513c173c.png&h=64608b19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據台媒，大S日前通過工作室宣佈因第三胎胚胎發育不全決定終止懷孕，她透露當時醫生給她的建議就是不要再使用藥物。對於這樣的結果她很難過，但也明白這非她所能控制，「老天爺順利給了我兩個孩子，已經是很大的恩賜了，謝謝大家的關心，我很平靜」。並強調，雖然跟這個孩子的緣分很短，但卻讓她體會很多，她相信好好珍惜此刻全家人在一起的溫暖時光，就是幸福。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12b1799fc6b9824ede3dffeec6a50272e9f09b6","tid":656444,"uid":82917,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:22:17.000Z","msg":"而家先知佢生左兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小玥兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6023bb3524946f14adfd5a9d7a867937a12d3045","tid":656444,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:26:11.000Z","msg":"發育不全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c12b2737cc3f9b9b4869cfe94426cf23c0495b9","tid":656444,"uid":82917,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"quote":{"pid":"6023bb3524946f14adfd5a9d7a867937a12d3045","tid":656444,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:26:11.000Z","msg":"發育不全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:26:44.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇得出佢勁鍾意bb"},{